connection protocol

application on phone
  until init is pressed, have an open socket waiting for a connection from the application
  if connection is made
    send variable information (gathered from class setup)
    once information is sent
      thread listening for variable change packets
      thread sending variable information packets
  if no connection is made
    read config file from phone and load variables with that information

application on computer
  attempt connection to application on phone
  once connection is made
    listen for variable information
    once all variables are recieved
      thread listening for variable change packets
      thread sending variable information to for writable values
